## 🔍 setting up the directory structure for a new DevOps project

> **Timestamp:** `2026-06-13 09:11:17`

### 01. `sudo mkdir -p /projects/devops/{scripts,logs,configs,backups}`

```bash
sudo mkdir -p /projects/devops/{scripts,logs,configs,backups}
```

**Output:**

```text
```

